<h1>Your Profile</h1>

Name: <%= @runner.name %><br><br>
Gender: <%= @runner.gender %><br><br>
Birthday:<%= @runner.birthday %><br><br>
Location: <%= @runner.location_city %>, <%= @runner.location_country %><br><br>
Experience Level: <%= @runner.experience_level %><br><br>

<%= button_to "EDIT", edit_runner_path(@runner), method: :get %>
<%= button_to "DELETE", runner_path(@runner), method: :delete %><br>

You have signed up for these races:
<ul>
<% @runner.races.each do |race| %>
    <li><%= link_to race.name, race_path(race) %></li>
    <% end %>
</ul>

You enrolled into these training plans:
<ul>
<% @runner.training_plans.each do |plan| %>
    <li><%= link_to plan.name, training_plan_path(plan) %></li>
    <% end %>
</ul>

<hr>
<%= link_to 'Back to home', home_path %>
